oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: WSM Freedom Train broadcast
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM coverage of the Freedom Train's stop in Nashville, TN. Announcer Jud Collins interviews Mayor Thomas L. Cummings and trainmaster Walter H. S. O'Brien. It is also mentioned that Russell Brothers and Secretary of State Joe C. Carr are present. Mistakenly labeled as 1947, the Freedom Train was in Nashville in 1948.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Opening statement (Jud Collins) -- Jud Collins introduces Thomas L. Cummings -- Thomas L. Cummings talks -- Jud Collins and Walter H. S. O'Brien talk -- Closing statement (Jud Collins)
